title: I am the descendant of the Divine Dragon!
description: I am the descendant of the Divine Dragon! Manhua I am the descendant of the Divine Dragon! – In the world of fierce competition among warriors on the Xuan Realm Continent, they refine their bodies, cultivate their martial meridians, seize the essence of heaven and earth, and strengthen themselves to surpass the limits of the mortal realm! Our warrior, Lu Hao, was unjustly targeted by his own clan since he was young. Fortunately, Lu Hao luckily awakens the bloodline of the Divine Dragon! From then on, with unwavering determination, he rises step by step amidst numerous threats, reaching the pinnacle of power! Unraveling the veils of mysteries from his past life! I, the Queen of Dragons! 我，神龙之后！ Wo, Shenlong Zhihou!
alternative_titles: I am the descendant of the Divine Dragon!
